WEBVTT

00:00:06.825 --> 00:00:09.101
Zamislite tople, meke kolačiće,

00:00:09.101 --> 00:00:10.513
hrskave slatkiše,

00:00:10.513 --> 00:00:12.076
baršunaste kolače,

00:00:12.076 --> 00:00:14.354
kornete pune sladoleda.

00:00:14.694 --> 00:00:16.580
Ide li vam slina na usta?

00:00:16.580 --> 00:00:17.538
Želite li desert?

00:00:17.538 --> 00:00:18.293
Zašto?

00:00:18.843 --> 00:00:19.924
Što se događa u mozgu

00:00:19.924 --> 00:00:22.840
da čini slatku hranu tako neodoljivom?

00:00:23.510 --> 00:00:24.421
Šećer je općeniti termin

00:00:24.421 --> 00:00:26.549
koji se koristi 
za opisivanje vrste molekula

00:00:26.549 --> 00:00:28.427
koje nazivamo ugljikohidrati,

00:00:28.427 --> 00:00:31.278
i nalazi se u različitim hranama i pićima.